TestNG -  Testing new generation frame work, unit test framework.
TDD framework ==  test driven development

Purpose--  design test cases in a systematic way
-- generate html report
--different annotation
--priorties/ sequence of execation of test casses
--dependencies
--grouping
--data provider 

testNG ==  open source, free and available in form of jar file

also called -- java unit testing framework
JE unit and testNG both are used only used in java , these both are java frame work

install testNG in Eclipse -- https://testng.org/testng-eclipse-update-site